## Conditions we treat

- Musculoskeletal (osteopathy): back and neck pain, headaches and migraines, joint pain and arthritis, posture imbalances, muscle tightness, sports injuries, sciatica, rib and pelvic pain.
- Pregnancy and paediatric (osteopathy): pregnancy-related lower back and pelvic pain, safe across all trimesters; infants and children for colic, feeding and sleep issues, growing pains, postural development.
- Pain and recovery (acupuncture): acute and chronic pain, tension headaches, migraines, post-injury recovery.
- Stress, sleep and mental wellbeing (acupuncture, herbal medicine): anxiety, insomnia, burnout, low mood, fatigue.
- Women's health (acupuncture, herbal medicine): menstrual irregularity, period pain, fertility support including IVF, perimenopause and menopause symptoms.
- Digestive and immune health (acupuncture, herbal medicine): IBS, bloating, reflux, nausea, low immunity.

